      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的拓扑图，核心是Etcd集群，但是得通过负载均衡器来访问。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
