    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "负载均衡器放在中间，两边都是Etcd集群。左边的是客户端视角的集群入口，右边的是实际的后端集群节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解成：左侧Etcd集群 → 经过负载均衡器 → 到右侧Etcd集群。这样画对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，三个节点从左到右：Etcd集群、负载均衡器、Etcd集群，用箭头连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，箭头方向好像有问题。应该是双向的，或者至少是负载均衡器指向右侧的Etcd集群，左侧的Etcd集群指向负载均衡器。现在看起来负载均衡器在中间，但连接关系不太对。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我检查一下——当前是左侧Etcd集群直接连到负载均衡器，然后负载均衡器连到右侧Etcd集群。您说的不对是指箭头方向反了，还是需要调整连接方式？",
